---
title: Fiery Mexican Beef Meatballs & Corn Rice with Bacon-Tomato Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Beef meatballs are lighting a fire of excitement with spices on popping corn rice. The secret to add that spark is a tomato salsa with golden bacon. It’s a firework of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65717bc138e51a4a51a30045-b25bd084.jpeg
